'''''Torture Observed: An Interview with Jabba's Cook''''' was a [[Book/Legends|book]] by [[Professor/Legends|Professors]] [[Ra Yasht]] and [[Skarten]] of [[Beshka University]] resulting from an interview with [[Porcellus/Legends|Porcellus]], [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba the Hutt's]] cook. The professors were able to gain access to the cook with the assistance of [[Darian Gli]], a member of Jabba's court, who was executed by Jabba following the book's publication. The success of their book compelled the Beshka University board to grant Ra Yasht and Skarten instant tenure.

